OL,3,CDisruption warning as Scottish Water
OL,4,Cstaff begin strike
OL,6,FScottish Water staff will stage a two-
OL,7,Fday strike amid a continued dispute
OL,8,Fover pay, amid warnings that repairs
OL,9,Fand water quality checks could be
OL,10,Fdisrupted.
OL,12,FWorkers will walk out on Tuesday and
OL,13,FWednesday following a one-day strike
OL,14,Flast month.
OL,16,FUnison, which represents more than
OL,17,F1,000 staff, warned that emergency
OL,18,Frepairs and water quality checks will
OL,19,Fnot be carried out during that time.
