OL,3,CDisruption warning as Scottish Water
OL,4,Cstaff begin strike
OL,6,FProblems reported with water supply,
OL,7,Fsewage or drainage also will not be
OL,8,Fdealt with until the strike is over,
OL,9,Fthe union added.
OL,11,FBut Scottish Water has said
OL,12,F"contingency plans are in place to
OL,13,Fenable us to maintain normal service."
OL,15,FThe union has rejected a 2.6% pay
OL,16,Foffer, amounting to at least #1,050,
OL,17,Fsaying it "fails to compensate staff
OL,18,Ffor a decade of real-term pay cuts."
